### providers
GET {{baseUrl}}/s3-viewer/api/v1/providers

### provider
@providerId = localstack
GET {{baseUrl}}/s3-viewer/api/v1/providers/{{providerId}}/buckets

### browse
@bucketName = demo-assets
GET {{baseUrl}}/s3-viewer/api/v1/providers/{{providerId}}/buckets/{{bucketName}}/browse?path=/

###
GET {{baseUrl}}/s3-viewer/api/v1/providers/{{providerId}}/buckets/{{bucketName}}/download?
    key={{$random.alphanumeric(8)}}

###
POST {{baseUrl}}/s3-viewer/api/v1/providers/{{providerId}}/buckets/{{bucketName}}/upload?
    path={{$random.alphanumeric(8)}}
    Content-Type: multipart/form-data

###
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/s3-viewer/api/v1/providers/{{providerId}}/buckets/{{bucketName}}/objects
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "keys": []
}

###
GET {{baseUrl}}/s3-viewer/api/v1/providers/{{providerId}}/buckets/{{bucketName}}/search?
    query={{$random.alphanumeric(8)}}&
    path={{$random.alphanumeric(8)}}&
    maxResults={{$random.integer(100)}}